ber of hours (the recordshe set on an especially memorable occasion was from one to eight). Hadthere been a Miss Russia and had the age of prize misses been prolonged tojust under thirty, beautiful Lyuba would have won the title. She was a tallwoman with slim ankles, big breasts, broad shoulders, and a pair of gay blueeyes in a round rosy face. Her auburn hair must have always felt as being ina state of imminent disarray for she constantly stroked its side wave, in agraceful elbow-raised gesture